{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's where they wanted us to perform best, because it was an important function for them, also.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one day, we come in, we thought this would be a great place to finish the war or just stay there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, one day, we were working on some detail and doing some kind of a ditch work or whatever, I never forget it, and when we got back, it was just totally destroyed.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Allies must have-- but the incredible part of it was that they bombed it when we were not there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So whatever their intelligence-- I mean, to this day, I'd like to believe that they did this knowingly that we were not in that factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because they did it in such a fast and furious fashion that when we got back, the factory was completely annihilated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so when we got back, there was nothing any more to work for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we continued on to another camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Augsburg, I was another four weeks, maybe five weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were just stopover camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I continued on to other little camps, which were created for strictly for work camps to do some specific things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I even saw these factory, whoever they were, bosses that would take us and bring us back to these places that we like, we did road work, cut trees, and that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one camp, I remember, I lived underground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- it was built under-- half of the building was underground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was warm, which was warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then, I went-- Then we started marching towards the Dachau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We marched.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no more-- there was no more trains after that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After, there was no more trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
